data.description: Own this home for UNDER $ 1000 a month.   Home qualifies for Stackable closing cost assistance.  Making this investment a great opportunity.  Live in one unit , use the rent to qualify for purchase and help  pay your mortgage along the way.... The 1st floor features 1 bed 2 baths,  finished basement with bonus room , updated center kitchen, access to the back yard,. The  2nd floor offers 1 bed 1 bath , large windows with plenty of natural lighting, and a traditional layout.   Each unit has separate Heaters, Hot Water Tanks, Electric Panels , and Gas Meters for easy management. Centrally located to area amenities, close to public transportation, 69th St Terminal, and close to shopping. The property is being sold in AS-IS condition.  Schedule your showing today !
